Full review comments:

- [P2] Keep the new runner passing pyright — /tmp/fdb-slice-10-20260621T221212Z/src/python/eval/d0b_parity_run.py:377-379
  With the repository typecheck gate enabled, `pyright src/python/eval/d0b_parity_run.py` fails because the dynamic `getattr` call is typed as returning `object` here; the same issue appears for `cost_block.setdefault` below. Since `agent-typecheck.sh` is a required gate, narrow/cast these dynamic helper results before calling `float()` or dict methods.

